+    r"\b(hold on|wait|listen|mods\b|focus|stay on topic|moving on|move on|next up|next|we'?re going|we are going|let'?s|keep it|no spoilers|don't ask|do not ask|please stop|lock in|everybody|everyone|you guys|y'?all)\b",
